text: Wolfenschiessen is a municipality of the canton of Nidwalden in Switzerland. The main sights of Wolfenschiessen are: the parish church St. Maria, the chapel St. Joder in Altzellen, the mansions Hechhuis, and the Grossitz mansion. == References == == Other websites == *Official Website of Wolfenschiessen Category:Municipalities of Nidwalden
